WEBVTT

00:14.640 --> 00:15.430
Xiao Wuyi?

00:32.070 --> 00:34.430
Where did he hide the divorce papers?

01:09.840 --> 01:11.570
What were you and Mao doing just now?

01:11.570 --> 01:12.430
Archery match.

01:12.760 --> 01:13.690
Between you two?

01:14.840 --> 01:16.100
Why the archery match?

01:17.680 --> 01:19.210
So who emerged victorious?

01:19.350 --> 01:20.350
What do you think?

01:22.110 --> 01:22.980
Well...

01:25.380 --> 01:26.590
Who do you hope ended up winning?

01:26.590 --> 01:29.340
As the Commander of the Beifu Army,
you competed with Mao in archery.

01:29.340 --> 01:30.800
You must've won unfairly.

01:37.340 --> 01:38.539
Where is my hairband?

01:39.289 --> 01:40.650
W-What hairband?

01:40.890 --> 01:41.940
The hairband I gave you

01:41.940 --> 01:44.340
for you to cover your eyes
during the match!

01:47.700 --> 01:48.560
I threw it away.

01:49.420 --> 01:51.750
You threw it away?
Who allowed you to do it?

01:56.890 --> 01:59.220
Didn't Xiao Wuyi say
he had thrown it away?

03:27.210 --> 03:31.050
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

03:31.420 --> 03:34.040
[Episode 14]

03:36.940 --> 03:39.410
Xiao Wuyi has gotten you
the travel permit.

03:42.620 --> 03:44.090
You only need to sign it.

03:49.780 --> 03:52.460
I wonder when I will be able
to come back here again.

03:52.460 --> 03:55.460
Actually, I quite like this place.

04:00.220 --> 04:05.120
[Palace of Eternal Peace]

04:17.810 --> 04:19.870
Brother, why do you want to keep them?

04:20.769 --> 04:21.810
Is it for

04:23.250 --> 04:24.890
that dancer named Chan?

04:26.500 --> 04:27.450
She does

04:27.980 --> 04:29.100
look somewhat

04:29.100 --> 04:30.250
like Jiayu.

04:32.010 --> 04:33.890
Take them
to the Directorate of Attendants.

04:33.890 --> 04:34.620
Understood.

04:38.570 --> 04:39.370
Brother,

04:40.570 --> 04:41.890
are you really willing

04:42.659 --> 04:43.860
to let Jiayu leave?

04:45.659 --> 04:46.920
Yaoyao loves freedom.

04:47.770 --> 04:48.690
Right now, I

04:49.940 --> 04:50.810
can't keep her.

04:52.250 --> 04:53.540
Wuyi also said that

04:54.740 --> 04:56.740
if I can bring peace and prosperity

04:57.250 --> 04:58.180
to Ye

04:58.890 --> 05:00.450
and turn the places Yaoyao loves

05:00.450 --> 05:01.620
into a paradise,

05:03.250 --> 05:05.310
that would also be a way of loving her.

05:08.770 --> 05:10.900
As long as I can seize the supreme power

05:11.180 --> 05:12.740
in this Jiankang Palace...

05:18.250 --> 05:20.380
she will definitely return to my side.

05:25.490 --> 05:27.860
[A few months later]

05:38.750 --> 05:42.220
[Beifu Army Barracks, Northern Border]

05:43.500 --> 05:45.100
How could I ever kill Xiuxiu?

05:45.370 --> 05:46.570
I grew up with her.

05:47.100 --> 05:48.250
I was waiting to save enough

05:48.250 --> 05:49.530
military pay to propose to her.

05:49.530 --> 05:51.200
[Guo Jiu, Beifu soldier]

05:49.659 --> 05:51.320
How could I possibly kill her?

05:56.180 --> 05:57.510
I can't control myself.

05:58.130 --> 05:59.300
I want to kill people.

05:59.300 --> 06:00.500
I want to hack people.

06:00.570 --> 06:01.770
I want to bite people!

06:02.330 --> 06:03.990
I've been consumed by a curse.

06:04.210 --> 06:05.540
Yes, a curse!

06:06.060 --> 06:07.860
This is a curse on the Beifu Army.

06:07.970 --> 06:09.770
Beifu shouldn't have reformed!

06:09.810 --> 06:10.890
God cast a curse.

06:11.180 --> 06:12.380
This is retribution!

06:12.420 --> 06:14.660
This is retribution!

06:24.210 --> 06:25.450
Including last night's incident,

06:25.450 --> 06:26.370
there have been 9 cases

06:26.370 --> 06:28.130
of soldiers going nuts and hurting people.

06:28.130 --> 06:29.190
Everyone says that

06:30.210 --> 06:32.300
this curse is aimed at the Beifu Reform.

06:32.300 --> 06:34.159
Nothing happens without a cause.

06:34.300 --> 06:35.830
Get Ruisheng over quickly.

06:43.980 --> 06:45.690
This is the cause of the disease.

06:45.690 --> 06:46.940
Stray dogs that eat this rice

06:46.940 --> 06:48.070
will end up this way.

06:48.100 --> 06:50.560
Berserk, out of control, and bloodthirsty.

06:50.659 --> 06:51.920
The onset time varies.

06:52.100 --> 06:53.980
Some fall ill right after consuming it.

06:53.980 --> 06:54.980
Others take 3 to 5 days.

06:54.980 --> 06:57.060
It's the rations allocated
by the imperial court from Guazhou.

06:57.060 --> 06:58.010
It's dark in color

06:58.010 --> 06:58.860
but not moldy.

06:59.570 --> 07:00.980
It looks like it was soaked in water.

07:00.980 --> 07:02.450
I once saw it in one

07:02.690 --> 07:04.890
of Jiayu's books about mining methods.

07:05.540 --> 07:07.870
Some people who drink water from the mines

07:08.050 --> 07:10.010
would fall into a coma
and become delirious.

07:10.010 --> 07:11.130
Long-term consumption

07:11.130 --> 07:13.130
would greatly affect one's lifespan.

07:13.130 --> 07:15.540
Although what's happening now is
not exactly the same,

07:15.540 --> 07:16.670
it's quite similar.

07:17.060 --> 07:18.060
But does Guazhou

07:18.740 --> 07:19.600
have any mines?

07:19.690 --> 07:21.690
No, I guess? I haven't heard of any.

07:22.180 --> 07:22.940
Guazhou.

07:25.180 --> 07:26.060
The Cui family.

07:29.130 --> 07:31.330
It's time to investigate the Cui family

07:31.620 --> 07:33.220
Empress Wenxi was born into.

07:39.210 --> 07:39.860
By the way.

07:41.980 --> 07:42.580
Your cure.

07:43.300 --> 07:43.810
Cure?

07:50.300 --> 07:53.210
Ruisheng, is everything going well
in the Northern Border?

07:53.210 --> 07:56.140
I heard winter is coming,
so remember to wrap up warm.

07:56.210 --> 07:58.420
My master and I improved
the steelmaking method recently

07:58.420 --> 08:00.660
and forged a new set
of medical needles for you.

08:00.660 --> 08:02.330
They should be thinner and tougher

08:02.330 --> 08:03.860
than those you usually use.

08:03.980 --> 08:05.770
I also made a mirror for Yuanji.

08:06.490 --> 08:08.540
It's not as good as a bronze one, though.

08:08.540 --> 08:10.300
My master is determined
to make caltrop fireballs.

08:10.300 --> 08:12.300
I plan to leave Jiankang
with him to look for ore.

08:12.300 --> 08:14.980
We'll go to Mount Tugao first,
and then head southwest.

08:14.980 --> 08:16.420
It's said to abound with bandits.

08:16.420 --> 08:18.950
It's a good chance
to test my lightness skill.

08:19.050 --> 08:20.310
She's messing around.

08:29.360 --> 08:30.480
How heartless.

08:34.450 --> 08:36.690
Do you think caltrop fireballs
really exist?

08:34.809 --> 08:37.230
[Outside of Lingfeng Fort, Guazhou]

08:37.059 --> 08:38.020
Could the things
recorded in these ancient texts

08:38.020 --> 08:39.059
just be made up?

08:40.090 --> 08:42.210
How could there be such a powerful ore?

08:42.210 --> 08:43.809
Once set aflame,
it can't be extinguished by water,

08:43.809 --> 08:44.730
blocking out the sun

08:44.730 --> 08:46.260
and leaving nothing alive.

08:46.730 --> 08:48.940
It definitely exists.

08:49.140 --> 08:49.660
Well...

08:50.380 --> 08:51.090
Please enjoy your meal.

08:51.090 --> 08:51.690
Thank you.

08:52.300 --> 08:53.360
If it didn't exist,

08:53.450 --> 08:55.780
why would the ancients record it in books?

08:56.660 --> 08:58.380
Would they just play a joke
on us later generations?

08:58.380 --> 08:59.060
Besides,

08:59.420 --> 09:00.690
as vast as the world is,

09:01.210 --> 09:03.180
how much of it have you actually seen?

09:03.180 --> 09:04.240
Speaking of which,

09:04.380 --> 09:05.540
I've traveled further and wider

09:05.540 --> 09:06.330
-than...
-Than

09:06.330 --> 09:07.570
my White ever has.

09:12.270 --> 09:13.750
Who is W-White?

09:17.730 --> 09:18.390
Woof, woof.

09:24.400 --> 09:25.210
Seriously,

09:25.230 --> 09:28.380
are you sure your mother is
in Lingfeng Fort?

09:28.940 --> 09:30.660
This is the fief of the Cuis,

09:30.660 --> 09:32.590
Empress Wenxi's maternal family.

09:32.610 --> 09:34.090
-You old wretch,
-Around here...

09:34.090 --> 09:35.090
do you want to die?

09:35.780 --> 09:36.210
Please don't.

09:36.210 --> 09:38.140
No monthly payment, no stall here!

09:38.420 --> 09:38.780
Hurry!

09:38.780 --> 09:39.980
In broad daylight...

09:40.420 --> 09:41.140
Take it out!

09:41.160 --> 09:42.830
I really don't have any.

09:47.300 --> 09:48.450
Madam, are you okay?

09:49.540 --> 09:50.780
I'm fine.

09:50.780 --> 09:51.610
You caused trouble again.

09:51.610 --> 09:52.810
Let's go! Run!

09:52.810 --> 09:55.470
Hey, what's wrong with me
fighting for justice?

09:57.420 --> 09:59.080
I don't want to do this either.

09:59.330 --> 10:00.810
I have no choice.

10:04.060 --> 10:04.720
You guys...

10:07.570 --> 10:08.570
Come on, smell it.

10:09.090 --> 10:09.950
Here, smell it.

10:11.540 --> 10:13.090
Let's go. Run quickly. Hurry!

10:13.090 --> 10:14.620
Who exactly are they after?

10:14.780 --> 10:16.380
Are they Northern Qin spies here
to catch you?

10:16.380 --> 10:17.060
Me?

10:18.090 --> 10:19.450
We agreed to go to Mount Tugao

10:19.450 --> 10:20.970
and only came here
after receiving your mother's letter.

10:20.970 --> 10:22.020
Who do you think they are after?

10:22.020 --> 10:22.660
Hurry! Let's go!

10:22.660 --> 10:23.260
Mother...

10:23.610 --> 10:24.870
My mother is in danger.

10:26.300 --> 10:27.490
Nanxing, hurry.

10:27.490 --> 10:29.620
Go find Xiao Wuyi immediately. Hurry.

10:30.260 --> 10:31.490
My Lady, I'm going then.

10:31.490 --> 10:32.050
Quickly!

10:32.050 --> 10:33.980
Let's go. We should run now. Hurry!

10:37.840 --> 10:38.730
[Cui Shi]

10:38.850 --> 10:39.380
I...

10:40.570 --> 10:41.430
Take them away.

10:42.950 --> 10:44.700
[Lingfeng Fort]

10:50.300 --> 10:51.100
Young Master.

10:52.210 --> 10:53.680
The Young Lady still refuses
to try on the wedding dress.

10:53.680 --> 10:56.450
[Cui Shao'an]

10:55.850 --> 10:56.650
You may leave.

10:58.810 --> 10:59.420
Foot.

11:03.490 --> 11:04.290
The other one.

11:07.460 --> 11:08.580
[Cui Lingyi]

11:12.060 --> 11:15.020
Do you really plan to stay
in the Cui family's place forever?

11:15.020 --> 11:16.170
This is Cui Mansion,

11:16.610 --> 11:17.570
my home.

11:17.900 --> 11:20.360
If you have a share,
I should have one as well.

11:21.090 --> 11:22.020
What do you mean?

11:22.690 --> 11:24.780
Do you insist on finding
a matrilocal husband?

11:24.780 --> 11:25.540
Cui Shao'an,

11:27.140 --> 11:28.330
all you want is to drive me

11:28.330 --> 11:29.590
out of the Cui Mansion,

11:29.810 --> 11:32.260
so you can hold sway
over the entire Cui family.

11:32.260 --> 11:33.300
Since childhood,

11:33.730 --> 11:35.260
be it studying or managing affairs,

11:35.260 --> 11:36.900
you're nowhere near as good as me.

11:36.900 --> 11:38.630
We are both Father's children.

11:38.660 --> 11:40.260
Why are you the Young Master?

11:40.420 --> 11:41.060
Lingyi,

11:41.970 --> 11:43.210
you are already going to marry Prince Qi.

11:43.210 --> 11:44.850
What else are you dissatisfied with?

11:44.850 --> 11:45.910
What's there about

11:46.450 --> 11:48.710
the Cui family that you're holding onto?

11:51.490 --> 11:53.550
There is nothing worth holding onto.

11:54.210 --> 11:55.570
I just don't want you

11:55.570 --> 11:56.850
to ruin the Cui family.

11:57.690 --> 11:58.490
Young Master.

11:59.630 --> 12:00.850
We have caught the person.

12:00.850 --> 12:03.110
Cui Shao'an, who did you catch this time?

12:05.180 --> 12:06.310
A beauty, of course.

12:06.660 --> 12:09.850
Cui Lingyi, the imperial edict
for your marriage has been issued.

12:09.850 --> 12:12.250
You have to leave
whether you want to or not.

12:32.260 --> 12:33.020
Where is she?

12:33.380 --> 12:35.330
She definitely hasn't
run out of Lingfeng Fort.

12:35.330 --> 12:37.590
I'll lead our men to search immediately.

12:37.730 --> 12:38.300
Go!

12:43.690 --> 12:45.150
Where did Yuan Xiaoliu go?

12:55.780 --> 12:56.940
Follow me out of the Fort!

12:56.940 --> 12:57.940
Search the entire Guazhou

12:57.940 --> 12:59.060
for her!

13:01.540 --> 13:03.610
Don't look so gloomy.

13:04.570 --> 13:05.810
Since you are already here,

13:05.810 --> 13:07.060
just settle down.

13:07.690 --> 13:08.570
In the future,

13:08.900 --> 13:11.700
you will all enjoy lives
of wealth and privileges.

13:12.940 --> 13:14.490
So be smart, all of you.

13:19.420 --> 13:21.540
Being chosen to serve the Young Master

13:21.540 --> 13:22.900
is your blessing.

13:23.690 --> 13:25.140
Cheer up, everyone!

13:28.090 --> 13:29.490
Stop pulling a long face!

13:30.540 --> 13:31.540
You'll be the one.

13:33.660 --> 13:34.810
So useless!

13:36.690 --> 13:38.350
Why did she faint from fright?

13:38.850 --> 13:42.140
It's said that those chosen
by the Young Master will suffer greatly.

13:42.140 --> 13:44.490
But working in the mines
in the back mountain is different.

13:44.490 --> 13:46.820
Lingfeng Fort provides food and clothes.

13:46.820 --> 13:49.450
And there's even a monthly allowance
to send to our families.

13:49.450 --> 13:51.570
Lingfeng Fort is indeed
running illegal private mines.

13:51.570 --> 13:54.100
Are all these girls
going to work in the mines?

13:54.380 --> 13:55.580
But why choose girls?

13:56.060 --> 13:57.380
Could Mother also be there?

13:57.380 --> 13:58.570
Why the long face?

14:06.380 --> 14:07.380
You'll be the one.

14:08.300 --> 14:10.360
Take the rest of them to the workshop.

14:12.180 --> 14:12.980
Young Master,

14:13.570 --> 14:15.780
she's the prettiest
among this batch of girls.

14:15.780 --> 14:17.980
I was just about to take her to your room.

14:26.970 --> 14:28.300
Turn your head this way.

14:37.900 --> 14:39.300
She is not much to look at,

14:39.900 --> 14:40.900
but I'll take her.

14:41.300 --> 14:42.450
Take her to my room.

14:43.570 --> 14:44.300
Understood.

14:48.940 --> 14:50.900
I'm Yang Zhang, the County Sheriff.
Greetings, Your Highness.

14:49.090 --> 14:51.120
[Hall of the County Sheriff's Mansion,
Guazhou]

14:53.090 --> 14:54.780
What brings you to Guazhou, Your Highness?

14:54.780 --> 14:56.180
Is it official business?

15:00.430 --> 15:02.210
Weird illnesses have been breaking out
across Guazhou,

15:02.210 --> 15:04.330
yet you didn't report
to the Imperial Medical Bureau.

15:04.330 --> 15:06.730
Instead, you murdered witnesses
and destroyed corpses.

15:04.400 --> 15:06.520
[Yang Zhang, Guazhou County Sheriff]

15:07.120 --> 15:07.850
Yang Zhang,

15:08.610 --> 15:10.180
if I were on official business here,

15:10.180 --> 15:12.210
you would've already been executed.

15:12.210 --> 15:13.210
I have no idea.

15:13.540 --> 15:14.660
I really don't know.

15:14.660 --> 15:17.520
How long are you going to keep covering
for the Cuis?

15:25.490 --> 15:27.090
I really have no idea!

15:29.970 --> 15:31.660
I'm only making a guess.

15:32.140 --> 15:34.850
The Cui family is
Empress Wenxi's maternal family,

15:34.850 --> 15:36.420
the top noble family in Ye,

15:36.570 --> 15:37.660
with deep roots.

15:38.090 --> 15:40.940
I'm merely a lowly County Sheriff.

15:41.610 --> 15:43.470
Where did the disease originate?

15:45.060 --> 15:45.920
Lingfeng Fort.

15:47.780 --> 15:50.900
The Cui family's granary is
located right in Lingfeng Fort.

15:50.900 --> 15:53.330
The mines are also in Lingfeng Fort.

15:56.140 --> 15:59.340
Since the Cui family is
Empress Wenxi's maternal family,

15:59.970 --> 16:01.610
when you took me to flee back then,

16:01.610 --> 16:03.540
why did you seek help from the Xiaos

16:03.570 --> 16:05.300
instead of turning to the Cuis?

16:05.810 --> 16:08.090
Why have you even hidden my existence

16:08.970 --> 16:10.610
from the Cui family over these years?

16:10.610 --> 16:12.470
Empress Wenxi was forced into it.

16:13.060 --> 16:14.970
She had just given birth

16:15.610 --> 16:17.740
when she heard of His Majesty's death.

16:18.060 --> 16:20.090
But she didn't intend
to give up the Capital.

16:20.090 --> 16:21.150
The noble families

16:22.090 --> 16:24.290
deliberately delayed sending troops.

16:24.420 --> 16:26.450
When the army reached the city gates,

16:26.450 --> 16:28.510
Cui Jun submitted a secret memorial,

16:29.490 --> 16:32.410
hoping that the Empress would
sacrifice her own family

16:32.410 --> 16:33.660
for the bigger picture.

16:33.660 --> 16:34.860
What bigger picture?

16:35.260 --> 16:36.990
To win over the noble families,

16:37.020 --> 16:38.900
she had to dispatch
the remaining Imperial Guards

16:38.900 --> 16:41.180
to escort these noble families
as they fled south.

16:41.180 --> 16:42.710
The Empress was left alone,

16:43.210 --> 16:44.670
with His Majesty's child,

16:45.380 --> 16:46.940
defending the Capital by herself.

16:46.940 --> 16:49.060
The nobles abandoned the Empress

16:49.060 --> 16:50.570
to save the Ye Empire.

16:50.570 --> 16:51.380
From then on,

16:51.810 --> 16:54.660
the Cui family rose to become
the head of the noble families.

16:54.660 --> 16:56.300
Your mother, Empress Wenxi,

16:56.730 --> 16:57.780
died at that time.

17:00.420 --> 17:01.020
Qing Long,

17:02.090 --> 17:04.339
report the news about Guazhou
to Jiankang immediately

17:04.339 --> 17:05.819
and send a secret letter
to the Eastern Palace—

17:05.819 --> 17:07.099
the Cui family is suspicious,

17:07.099 --> 17:08.250
and the marriage needs to be reconsidered.

17:08.250 --> 17:09.619
Find an excuse to put it off.

17:09.619 --> 17:10.349
Understood.

17:13.050 --> 17:13.690
Nanxing?

17:15.380 --> 17:16.240
Your Highness,

17:16.490 --> 17:18.020
please save our Young Lady.

17:18.099 --> 17:19.859
The Cui family tricked her
into coming here

17:19.859 --> 17:20.859
and caught her.

17:20.859 --> 17:22.970
Weren't she and Yuan Xiaoliu
supposed to go to Mount Tugao?

17:22.970 --> 17:24.010
Why did they end up in Guazhou?

17:24.010 --> 17:25.530
That was the original plan.

17:25.530 --> 17:27.490
But Her Ladyship
received a letter from the Princess.

17:27.490 --> 17:28.240
The Princess said

17:28.240 --> 17:30.210
there were black-radiance ores here
that she once looked for

17:30.210 --> 17:31.730
and invited her to take a look.

17:31.730 --> 17:33.140
Yet she fell into a trap

17:33.140 --> 17:34.340
after arriving here.

17:34.580 --> 17:36.420
What did the Cuis capture Xie Jiayu for?

17:36.420 --> 17:38.350
The Cuis not only run illegal mines

17:38.420 --> 17:40.580
but also kidnapped
the Princess and Xie Jiayu.

17:40.580 --> 17:41.900
They must be up to something else.

17:41.900 --> 17:43.290
You two get ready and follow me

17:43.290 --> 17:44.580
into Lingfeng Fortress right away.

17:44.580 --> 17:46.580
Your Highness, you must be careful.

17:46.770 --> 17:48.450
The nobles' forts are
always heavily guarded.

17:48.450 --> 17:49.450
How will we get in?

17:52.210 --> 17:53.690
We'll walk in aboveboard.

17:59.180 --> 18:00.180
What's your name?

18:00.900 --> 18:01.450
My name is...

18:01.450 --> 18:02.050
Forget it.

18:02.380 --> 18:04.050
It doesn't matter
what your name used to be.

18:04.050 --> 18:04.940
From today on,

18:05.050 --> 18:05.980
you'll be called

18:06.490 --> 18:07.090
Yueniang.

18:08.380 --> 18:10.100
Singing, dancing, or whatever—

18:10.100 --> 18:11.430
just show me something.

18:11.970 --> 18:12.900
I don't know how.

18:12.940 --> 18:14.490
I've always hated
composing poetry or couplets

18:14.490 --> 18:15.540
just to put on airs.

18:15.540 --> 18:18.490
And I abhor
"Admonitions for Women" even more.

18:23.050 --> 18:23.860
How about...

18:25.210 --> 18:26.610
I do a magic trick for you?

18:39.250 --> 18:40.860
I've never seen any woman,

18:41.620 --> 18:43.660
no, anyone,

18:44.730 --> 18:47.100
solve the Nine-Linked Rings
faster than you.

18:47.100 --> 18:48.210
It's nothing.

18:48.210 --> 18:49.210
I know a lot more.

18:49.210 --> 18:50.940
If you have anything else
you want me to solve,

18:50.940 --> 18:51.870
just bring it on.

18:52.100 --> 18:54.620
You're so much better
than those noble ladies.

18:54.620 --> 18:56.420
When I send you to the imperial palace,

18:56.420 --> 18:58.010
you can compete with my sister.

18:58.010 --> 19:00.210
Hold on, hold on... The imperial palace?

19:00.210 --> 19:01.820
You want me to go to the imperial palace
with your sister?

19:01.820 --> 19:03.420
Aren't you hurting her this way?

19:03.420 --> 19:05.730
It's her own fault
for always going against me.

19:05.730 --> 19:07.730
She has to meddle in everything I do.

19:08.180 --> 19:09.620
It's nice to have someone
care about what you do.

19:09.620 --> 19:11.100
Unlike me, no one keeps me in check.

19:11.100 --> 19:13.660
I have suffered so much in my life.

19:15.140 --> 19:16.450
Given your status,

19:16.820 --> 19:18.680
who would dare to make you suffer?

19:19.900 --> 19:20.530
Pardon?

19:20.660 --> 19:22.720
Do you know, in these troubled times,

19:23.290 --> 19:25.290
how much money it costs to maintain

19:25.490 --> 19:27.620
such beautiful black hair like yours?

19:27.970 --> 19:31.010
It symbolizes a life of abundance
only someone who's never

19:31.010 --> 19:33.270
suffered from cold or hunger could live.

19:33.770 --> 19:36.100
You're a girl raised in wealth and luxury.

19:36.140 --> 19:39.210
Yet our Lingfeng Fortress
only takes in refugee girls,

19:40.100 --> 19:43.580
who know nothing about singing,
dancing, or Nine-Linked Rings.

19:43.580 --> 19:45.140
They can't even afford food.

19:45.140 --> 19:46.860
Someone as versatile

19:47.010 --> 19:48.620
and healthy as you

19:49.290 --> 19:50.820
is the first we've ever had.

19:54.820 --> 19:55.420
Tell me.

19:56.580 --> 19:57.290
Who are you?

19:57.530 --> 19:58.050
I...

19:58.360 --> 20:00.140
I'm indeed not a refugee.

20:00.580 --> 20:01.370
I am...

20:02.660 --> 20:03.620
C-Come closer.

20:09.140 --> 20:10.490
I am the envoy from the Eastern Palace,

20:10.490 --> 20:11.900
Da, the Right Imperial Guard.

20:11.900 --> 20:13.760
Greetings, Prince Qi's Consort.

20:14.100 --> 20:15.230
I'm not married yet.

20:15.340 --> 20:16.940
You can just call me Lady Cui.

20:17.290 --> 20:18.010
Lady Cui,

20:18.490 --> 20:19.290
these are

20:19.290 --> 20:20.890
all gifts from His Highness.

20:21.210 --> 20:22.810
Hope they are to your liking.

20:55.860 --> 20:57.210
There's no trace of Lady Xie.

20:57.210 --> 20:58.100
I haven't found her either,

20:58.100 --> 20:59.700
nor have I found the dungeon.

21:01.690 --> 21:03.180
The new concubine the Young Master took

21:03.180 --> 21:04.380
is way too demanding.

21:04.820 --> 21:06.180
She even asked us to split a bamboo

21:06.180 --> 21:07.510
into 100 bamboo strips.

21:07.900 --> 21:09.760
She's clearly just torturing us.

21:10.140 --> 21:11.400
What water filtering?

21:11.450 --> 21:13.910
I think she's just fooling
the Young Master.

21:16.100 --> 21:19.430
You continue to investigate
the defenses in Lingfeng Fort.

21:22.050 --> 21:23.910
Here are the things you asked for.

21:25.380 --> 21:26.780
Where should we put them?

21:31.690 --> 21:33.380
Just put them anywhere here.

21:56.100 --> 21:56.500
You...

21:58.250 --> 21:58.900
It's me.

22:01.020 --> 22:02.180
I know it's you.

22:03.900 --> 22:05.730
How did you know I came to Lingfeng Fort?

22:05.730 --> 22:08.330
The Eastern Palace's envoy,
Da, who can speak.

22:08.490 --> 22:10.020
Who else could it be but you?

22:10.620 --> 22:11.580
But I didn't expect

22:11.580 --> 22:12.780
you to be here so soon.

22:13.170 --> 22:14.520
It should take at least 6 or 7 days

22:14.520 --> 22:15.870
to get here from Beifu, right?

22:15.870 --> 22:17.250
A strange disease broke out in Beifu,

22:17.250 --> 22:18.660
and it's related to Guazhou.

22:18.660 --> 22:19.820
I ran into Nanxing

22:19.820 --> 22:20.950
on my first day here.

22:21.380 --> 22:23.180
She said you asked her to find me.

22:23.820 --> 22:24.940
I'm really lucky.

22:26.380 --> 22:27.290
You're already locked up here.

22:27.290 --> 22:28.950
How can you call that "lucky"?

22:29.010 --> 22:29.490
I...

22:43.140 --> 22:45.270
How did you manage to fool Cui Shao'an?

22:45.690 --> 22:46.690
Actually,

22:46.820 --> 22:48.580
I didn't succeed at first.

22:52.620 --> 22:54.420
Since you've found out about it,

22:54.690 --> 22:56.290
I'll just be honest with you.

22:57.730 --> 22:59.180
Have you ever heard about

23:00.100 --> 23:02.730
the position of Tomb-excavating General
established by Cao Bao?

23:02.730 --> 23:05.380
We are all descendants
of the Tomb Raiders.

23:09.050 --> 23:10.980
I am the 6th-generation successor

23:11.490 --> 23:12.580
of Tomb Raiders.

23:14.820 --> 23:16.020
You don't believe me?

23:16.050 --> 23:17.770
You wouldn't want us to "visit"

23:17.770 --> 23:19.650
the Cui family's graves, would you?

23:19.650 --> 23:20.850
Your grandfather's,

23:21.140 --> 23:22.010
your father's,

23:23.180 --> 23:24.430
or yours?

23:25.690 --> 23:26.290
You know what?

23:26.290 --> 23:27.420
We Tomb Raiders

23:27.420 --> 23:28.150
have nothing

23:28.250 --> 23:29.100
but patience.

23:29.380 --> 23:31.180
I can wait for a few decades,

23:31.290 --> 23:31.900
you know,

23:31.900 --> 23:33.530
and I'll dig up
your entire family's tombs.

23:33.530 --> 23:34.820
-All of them...
-Enough.

23:34.820 --> 23:35.550
Little girl,

23:36.530 --> 23:37.860
do you think I'm stupid?

23:41.290 --> 23:42.340
F-Fine, alright.

23:43.770 --> 23:44.490
I admit that

23:45.010 --> 23:47.490
I saw your family
running illegal private mines.

23:47.490 --> 23:48.970
But I know the rules of the trade.

23:48.970 --> 23:50.180
I won't say a single word

23:50.180 --> 23:51.910
about what I shouldn't reveal.

23:52.820 --> 23:54.140
But we tomb raiders

23:54.180 --> 23:55.180
want a share of what we see,

23:55.180 --> 23:55.730
you know?

23:57.290 --> 23:59.020
Why do you still not believe me?

23:59.050 --> 23:59.530
I...

24:01.380 --> 24:02.620
Has anyone fainted

24:02.770 --> 24:04.940
or become berserk or manic all of a sudden

24:04.940 --> 24:07.010
in your family's mines recently?

24:16.770 --> 24:18.170
How did you know about it?

24:18.860 --> 24:20.250
I know a lot.

24:20.970 --> 24:22.430
It's because of the water.

24:26.620 --> 24:27.880
Do you want to solve it?

24:30.180 --> 24:31.250
I can help you.

24:31.820 --> 24:33.020
And the "concubine"?

24:33.690 --> 24:34.750
What's that about?

24:35.540 --> 24:38.170
It's nothing but an excuse.

24:38.420 --> 24:40.420
I promised to help him filter water.

24:40.490 --> 24:42.890
So I could stall
until you came here, right?

24:43.820 --> 24:44.620
Did you

24:45.250 --> 24:46.580
send Nanxing to find me?

24:46.770 --> 24:48.500
Didn't I already tell you that?

24:49.490 --> 24:50.340
Why?

24:50.860 --> 24:53.190
This place is clearly closer to Jiankang.

24:53.690 --> 24:55.900
Because you can use martial arts.

25:04.820 --> 25:05.970
What's wrong, Xiao Wuyi?

25:05.970 --> 25:07.500
It's debilitating powder.

25:10.380 --> 25:11.620
Xiao Wuyi, stop joking around.

25:11.620 --> 25:12.750
If you're affected,

25:12.900 --> 25:14.660
why am I... Why am I perfectly fine?

25:14.660 --> 25:16.190
You can't use martial arts,

25:16.210 --> 25:18.270
so of course you don't feel anything.

25:18.290 --> 25:19.290
Just as expected,

25:20.730 --> 25:21.860
you know each other.

25:25.900 --> 25:27.530
Do you really think I believed

25:27.530 --> 25:29.190
all that nonsense you told me?

25:29.210 --> 25:30.340
I just wanted to see

25:30.820 --> 25:33.100
what tricks you were going to play.

25:33.860 --> 25:35.100
But I have to admit that

25:35.100 --> 25:37.500
I was indeed interested
in the water filter

25:38.660 --> 25:40.050
you talked about.

25:40.050 --> 25:41.290
I swear I didn't lie to you about that.

25:41.290 --> 25:43.010
-I can really make the filter...
-Hold on.

25:43.010 --> 25:43.820
One at a time.

25:44.010 --> 25:45.250
Let's start with this one.

25:45.250 --> 25:47.660
Impersonating an envoy
from the Eastern Palace,

25:47.660 --> 25:49.050
you must have an extraordinary identity.

25:49.050 --> 25:51.100
How should I address you?

25:52.860 --> 25:53.660
Xiao Wuyi.

25:55.580 --> 25:57.040
I've heard a lot about you.

25:59.690 --> 26:00.290
Oh, no.

26:00.730 --> 26:02.460
This is bad. This is really bad.

26:03.690 --> 26:05.750
Even the Beifu Army has been alerted.

26:06.010 --> 26:06.470
Well...

26:06.970 --> 26:07.970
Then wouldn't the secret

26:07.970 --> 26:09.770
about Lingfeng Fort be exposed?

26:12.900 --> 26:14.230
So there's no other way.

26:14.340 --> 26:15.770
I can only silence you.

26:16.450 --> 26:16.970
I...

26:18.210 --> 26:18.810
Take this!

26:26.340 --> 26:27.690
Why is he so talkative?

26:28.780 --> 26:30.350
That's why I sealed his mouth.

26:30.350 --> 26:32.010
He can't move his body either?

26:33.140 --> 26:34.800
I learned this from Ruisheng.

26:35.100 --> 26:37.100
I have sealed off all his meridians.

26:37.180 --> 26:38.710
Now, he's basically frozen

26:38.940 --> 26:41.070
except for his eyes being able to move.

26:41.210 --> 26:42.010
Awesome.

26:42.580 --> 26:44.690
How long have you learned it
from Ruisheng?

26:44.690 --> 26:46.350
This is my first time doing it.

26:47.250 --> 26:49.530
I only watched it once.

26:50.010 --> 26:51.670
If I inserted it incorrectly,

26:51.770 --> 26:53.030
he could be paralyzed.

26:55.820 --> 26:57.450
What now? I'm leaving.

26:57.580 --> 26:58.140
Hold on.

26:58.250 --> 27:00.380
Do you know
where the Lingfeng Fort's mines are?

27:00.380 --> 27:01.580
In the back mountain.

27:01.860 --> 27:03.010
But for some reason,

27:03.180 --> 27:05.450
all the miners
they recruit here are girls.

27:05.450 --> 27:08.250
Statistics of refugees everywhere
only count adult males.

27:08.250 --> 27:09.050
Girls

27:10.970 --> 27:12.230
can be very deceptive.

27:13.010 --> 27:13.970
Yeah.

27:14.490 --> 27:15.490
At worst, he'd only be known

27:15.490 --> 27:18.020
as a lecherous Young Master
of the Cui family.

27:19.580 --> 27:21.490
How long will this acupuncture last?

27:21.490 --> 27:22.050
No idea.

27:22.490 --> 27:23.940
But when Ruisheng did it,

27:24.140 --> 27:25.870
that chicken lay there all day.

27:26.510 --> 27:28.240
Then we'll leave it to his fate.

27:28.620 --> 27:29.150
Let's go.

27:46.290 --> 27:46.860
Are you okay?

27:46.860 --> 27:48.250
Who is holding up whom?

27:49.970 --> 27:51.420
My bad. I'll hold you up.

27:51.820 --> 27:52.420
Let's go.

27:52.940 --> 27:53.470
Let's go.

28:04.140 --> 28:05.070
Don't be afraid.

28:11.050 --> 28:12.450
Mining can cause deaths,

28:13.010 --> 28:15.210
but how could so many people end up dead?

28:15.730 --> 28:16.900
After the Beifu soldiers ate

28:16.900 --> 28:18.660
the rice soaked in the mine water,

28:18.660 --> 28:20.690
they instantly went mad, lost their minds,

28:20.690 --> 28:22.820
and wanted to hurt people like beasts.

28:24.050 --> 28:26.900
The mine water does make people
go mad and lose their minds,

28:26.900 --> 28:29.290
but this is the first time
I've seen it lead to violence.

28:29.290 --> 28:31.690
This is no ordinary iron ore.

28:32.970 --> 28:35.030
Let's get out of Lingfeng Fort first.

28:38.010 --> 28:39.410
Let me help you. Let's go.

28:46.820 --> 28:48.690
Where are you going, General?

28:49.340 --> 28:50.180
Lady Cui?

28:56.100 --> 28:58.340
So she is Mao's future wife.

29:02.420 --> 29:03.420
Fly, come on.

29:03.690 --> 29:04.340
I'm ready.

29:04.340 --> 29:07.100
The drug hasn't worn off yet. I can't fly.

29:09.730 --> 29:12.660
You two, would you like to come back
with me for a chat?

29:19.940 --> 29:22.180
Brother, I think this robe is better.

29:22.490 --> 29:23.900
That one is a bit too ornate

29:23.900 --> 29:25.030
and lacks elegance.

29:25.970 --> 29:26.630
You decide.

29:27.010 --> 29:27.620
Brother,

29:28.050 --> 29:29.730
you usually like to wear

29:29.730 --> 29:30.970
light-colored clothes,

29:30.970 --> 29:33.530
but I think you look better in dark red.

29:34.100 --> 29:35.960
It gives you a more dignified air.

29:36.380 --> 29:37.240
Either is fine.

29:40.490 --> 29:43.940
Brother, my sister-in-law is
about to enter the imperial palace.

29:43.940 --> 29:45.400
You need to prepare early.

29:52.530 --> 29:53.210
Brother,

29:53.730 --> 29:55.730
I know you are unwilling to accept it,

29:55.730 --> 29:58.290
but if the marriage alliance goes wrong,

29:59.250 --> 30:00.660
it will backfire.

30:04.140 --> 30:05.820
I know you're worried about me.

30:05.820 --> 30:07.010
You don't need to worry.

30:07.010 --> 30:08.940
You should care about your own affairs.

30:08.940 --> 30:10.400
What about your marriage?

30:10.490 --> 30:11.180
Me?

30:11.900 --> 30:13.100
I won't marry anyone.

30:13.900 --> 30:15.630
I just want to stay by your side.

30:16.170 --> 30:17.050
Nonsense.

30:23.930 --> 30:25.260
-Master.
-Grand Tutor.

30:25.660 --> 30:26.520
Your Highness.

30:26.730 --> 30:27.600
You may leave.

30:28.820 --> 30:29.550
Understood.

30:34.690 --> 30:35.290
Master.

30:35.580 --> 30:38.510
Your Highness,
are you trying on the wedding attire?

30:39.060 --> 30:41.720
I'm tired these days.
I'll try it on another day.

30:42.010 --> 30:43.740
It doesn't matter if you don't.

30:47.380 --> 30:48.110
What's this?

30:51.490 --> 30:53.100
The Cui family runs
an illegal private mine,

30:53.100 --> 30:55.560
causing a strange disease
in the Beifu Army.

30:55.770 --> 30:58.100
Young Lord Xiao has submitted a memorial.

30:58.540 --> 31:00.690
County Sheriff Yang Zhang is the witness.

31:00.690 --> 31:02.010
There's solid evidence.

31:02.010 --> 31:03.580
The engagement with one of the Cuis

31:03.580 --> 31:07.180
is merely a means to prevent
the Princess's political marriage.

31:09.050 --> 31:13.620
A pawn is sometimes
like a piece of clothing.

31:13.690 --> 31:15.250
After it's used and worn,

31:15.860 --> 31:18.290
it should be thrown away.

31:22.690 --> 31:25.940
The Cui family will fall in a few days.

31:27.050 --> 31:29.420
But the Cui family is
the top noble family in Ye.

31:29.420 --> 31:30.550
That was in the past.

31:31.100 --> 31:33.620
I will never allow
another woman from the Cuis

31:33.620 --> 31:35.690
to become the future Empress of Ye.

31:39.140 --> 31:39.660
Fine.

31:40.290 --> 31:42.890
I will go seize and seal
the Cui Mansion myself.

31:43.970 --> 31:47.830
The Empress Dowager won't allow you
to mobilize the Imperial Guards.

31:58.100 --> 31:59.380
Your Highness,
you think this alone

31:59.380 --> 32:01.600
can make me mobilize
the troops of Prince Jing'an's Household

32:01.600 --> 32:03.460
in the name of the Heir's Consort?

32:03.970 --> 32:04.540
Yes.

32:05.290 --> 32:06.940
Someone at the imperial court is already

32:06.940 --> 32:08.140
using the Beifu curse

32:08.140 --> 32:09.070
to impeach Wuyi.

32:09.580 --> 32:11.660
Not to mention that Wuyi has
entered Lingfeng Fort.

32:11.660 --> 32:13.660
This is a life-or-death situation.

32:14.660 --> 32:16.170
I can't command the Imperial Guards
as they're

32:16.170 --> 32:17.820
under the Empress Dowager's control.

32:17.820 --> 32:20.150
But tonight, I must seize the Cui Mansion.

32:20.720 --> 32:24.140
But if you can't find evidence
of the Cui family's illegal private mines,

32:24.140 --> 32:26.420
you're dragging Prince Jing'an's Household
down with you.

32:26.420 --> 32:27.820
We can only take a gamble.

32:28.550 --> 32:30.350
Xiao Wuyi is also gambling on it.

32:32.180 --> 32:34.340
I can lend you the men.

32:40.620 --> 32:41.420
Brother Xiao.

32:42.290 --> 32:43.750
I dare not be addressed so.

32:44.380 --> 32:45.100
I believe

32:45.660 --> 32:47.320
Wuyi never misjudges anyone.

32:47.930 --> 32:49.660
Since he acknowledges you,
Your Highness, as Master,

32:49.660 --> 32:51.770
I believe you're of one mind with Wuyi

32:52.180 --> 32:53.310
and the Xiao family.

32:53.860 --> 32:54.820
You can borrow

32:56.180 --> 32:57.100
our troops.

32:59.620 --> 33:00.620
If I ever fail you,

33:00.900 --> 33:01.770
I, Li Yizhi,

33:02.490 --> 33:04.420
will die without a terrible death.

33:09.250 --> 33:09.970
Today,

33:10.290 --> 33:12.580
with the token of the Heir's Consort,
I'm ordering you

33:12.580 --> 33:13.490
to follow Prince Qi

33:13.490 --> 33:15.420
and secretly seal
the Cui Mansion in Jiankang.

33:15.420 --> 33:18.350
You're all at the command
of His Highness, Prince Qi.

33:18.940 --> 33:20.540
-Understood!
-Understood!

33:35.050 --> 33:35.910
Your Highness.

33:37.340 --> 33:38.860
I'm giving this token to you.

33:38.860 --> 33:39.990
From this moment on,

33:40.250 --> 33:42.860
these troops are at your command.

33:49.650 --> 33:54.450
-We'll follow your orders, Your Highness!
-We'll follow your orders, Your Highness!

34:01.180 --> 34:01.770
Three.

34:02.490 --> 34:03.290
Master,

34:03.730 --> 34:04.730
as you expected,

34:05.380 --> 34:08.340
Prince Qi has obtained the troops
of Prince Jing'an's Household

34:08.340 --> 34:10.199
and is heading to the Cui Mansion.

34:13.820 --> 34:14.820
It seems that

34:15.489 --> 34:19.570
Jiankang will be in chaos again tonight.

34:21.420 --> 34:22.010
Master,

34:22.500 --> 34:24.100
is it a bit too late to take out

34:24.420 --> 34:25.820
the betrothal gifts now?

34:26.449 --> 34:27.530
After tonight,

34:27.530 --> 34:30.739
the Cui family and Prince Qi
will surely be bitter enemies.

34:30.739 --> 34:33.130
These are betrothal gifts
prepared for Prince Qi.

34:33.130 --> 34:35.190
Who said they were for the Cui family?

34:37.650 --> 34:39.340
It has been 22 years.

34:40.340 --> 34:42.130
Cui Jun has hidden so deeply.

34:44.449 --> 34:46.900
Don't worry, they are all following.

34:49.610 --> 34:50.300
Brother,

34:51.300 --> 34:54.260
we should have a death squad of our own.

34:57.970 --> 34:58.780
Brother!

34:59.220 --> 35:02.050
You must have a death squad of your own,

35:02.700 --> 35:04.360
one that belongs to no one else

35:04.530 --> 35:05.530
but only to you.

35:08.610 --> 35:09.340
Lejun,

35:10.260 --> 35:11.120
are you scared?

35:15.050 --> 35:15.820
Brother,

35:16.970 --> 35:18.780
other noble families will also have

35:18.780 --> 35:20.980
what Prince Jing'an's Household owns.

35:21.490 --> 35:23.420
Today's Imperial Guards are weak.

35:23.890 --> 35:25.380
Otherwise, Prince Changsha wouldn't

35:25.380 --> 35:27.530
have broken through
the palace gates so easily back then.

35:27.530 --> 35:28.130
We...

35:33.900 --> 35:34.530
Really?

35:38.130 --> 35:39.790
Since we are joining the game,

35:40.130 --> 35:41.530
we can no longer be pawns.

35:44.570 --> 35:45.700
Don't worry, Lejun.

35:46.650 --> 35:48.530
I am learning to be a player.

35:50.090 --> 35:50.890
I will never be

35:52.420 --> 35:55.280
manipulated by anyone again
for the rest of my life.

36:10.260 --> 36:11.090
But tonight,

36:12.420 --> 36:14.820
it's more appropriate
to leave it to the men

36:15.340 --> 36:17.140
of Prince Jing'an's Household.

36:30.340 --> 36:32.860
Today, we're luring the Cui family
into the trap

36:32.860 --> 36:35.390
and using Xiao Wuyi
and the Beifu Army as bait.

36:35.570 --> 36:38.300
I only want to see if the Cui family would

36:39.090 --> 36:41.130
dig their own grave.

36:45.530 --> 36:46.260
Prince Qi?

36:46.900 --> 36:47.900
How come it's you?

36:48.490 --> 36:49.380
It's nothing.

36:50.490 --> 36:53.090
I just thought about
how unpleasant my previous visits

36:53.090 --> 36:54.490
to the Cui Mansion were.

36:54.970 --> 36:56.610
Now I want to vent my anger,

36:57.270 --> 36:58.420
so I came here.

36:58.650 --> 37:00.130
The Cui family and your family

37:00.130 --> 37:01.930
are having a marriage alliance.

37:02.170 --> 37:04.570
Now you've raided
the Cui Mansion at night.

37:04.700 --> 37:05.900
Aren't you afraid the ruined marriage

37:05.900 --> 37:07.900
will turn you into a laughingstock?

37:15.820 --> 37:16.820
Your Highness!

37:21.220 --> 37:23.340
The Cuis incited rumors
of the Beifu curse,

37:23.340 --> 37:24.820
attempting to sabotage the reform.

37:24.820 --> 37:26.610
Their crimes are unforgivable.

37:26.610 --> 37:28.900
Now, seize everyone in the Cui Mansion.

37:29.380 --> 37:30.530
Dead or alive,

37:31.170 --> 37:33.500
no one is allowed
to leave the Cui Mansion.

37:33.900 --> 37:34.900
-Understood!
-Understood!

37:34.900 --> 37:36.010
Do you have any evidence?

37:36.010 --> 37:36.780
Evidence?

37:39.340 --> 37:41.070
That depends on what we can find

37:41.380 --> 37:43.380
in the Cui Mansion tonight.

37:55.970 --> 37:58.220
I've wanted to do this for many years.

38:00.340 --> 38:01.420
What a pity.

38:03.050 --> 38:05.250
You've survived for over a decade more.

38:18.040 --> 38:20.690
[Lingfeng Fort]

38:21.380 --> 38:22.940
"Tomb Raider"?

38:24.300 --> 38:25.340
Do you really think

38:25.340 --> 38:27.570
I'm as stupid as my foolish brother

38:28.050 --> 38:29.070
and don't know you actually are

38:29.070 --> 38:31.270
Grand Tutor Xie's daughter, Xie Jiayu?

38:31.650 --> 38:35.050
I heard that you are Prince Qi's beloved

38:35.050 --> 38:37.940
and later married
the Heir of Prince Jing'an, Xiao Wuyi.

38:37.940 --> 38:38.970
Now,

38:39.220 --> 38:41.050
you are in a secret relationship

38:41.050 --> 38:42.450
with this guard named Da.

38:43.700 --> 38:46.170
You're really something.

38:47.860 --> 38:48.460
Let her go!

38:52.150 --> 38:54.020
Chug down this drug,

38:54.880 --> 38:56.000
and I'll let her go.

38:56.650 --> 38:57.980
What are you going to do?

39:02.450 --> 39:03.180
Are you okay?

39:03.450 --> 39:05.450
This is the strongest aphrodisiac.

39:06.090 --> 39:08.780
As strong and vigorous as he is,

39:09.420 --> 39:11.080
it's perfect for him, I think.

39:11.260 --> 39:12.120
How do you feel?

39:13.340 --> 39:14.050
Tell me.

39:14.740 --> 39:16.050
Who on earth are you?

39:16.780 --> 39:18.820
Where are your two accomplices?

39:19.210 --> 39:21.650
What are you up to in Lingfeng Fort?

39:24.530 --> 39:25.790
Eldest Young Lady Cui,

39:26.940 --> 39:29.270
how long
are you going to keep up this show?

39:30.260 --> 39:32.010
If you truly wanted to hurt us,

39:32.600 --> 39:35.170
why didn't you just hand us over
to Cui Shao'an?

39:35.170 --> 39:37.380
This aphrodisiac is just
a blood-invigorating medicine.

39:37.380 --> 39:38.260
Added with Chuanxiong,

39:38.260 --> 39:40.380
it can cause a temporary surge
of qi and blood,

39:40.380 --> 39:42.440
but it also has a detoxifying effect.

39:42.740 --> 39:44.070
You are not a bad person.

39:49.860 --> 39:52.790
Young Lord Xiao,
you didn't show your true identity.

39:53.230 --> 39:55.360
So how could you expect me to be honest?

39:57.090 --> 39:58.050
You know who I am?

39:58.610 --> 39:59.900
What exactly do you want?

39:59.900 --> 40:01.900
I want you to destroy the Cui family.

40:03.700 --> 40:06.130
But you are about to marry
into the Crown Prince's family.

40:06.130 --> 40:07.820
I assume you have also seen

40:07.820 --> 40:09.450
the girls in the mines.

40:09.970 --> 40:11.380
The crimes committed by my father

40:11.380 --> 40:13.420
will come to light sooner or later.

40:13.650 --> 40:14.700
By then,

40:14.780 --> 40:17.170
the Cui family,
the top noble family in the world,

40:17.170 --> 40:18.700
will be utterly doomed.

40:19.610 --> 40:20.940
So I'd like to ask you two

40:21.130 --> 40:23.860
to help our Cui family
return to the right path.

40:24.420 --> 40:25.900
Why should we trust you?

40:29.820 --> 40:31.550
It's my mother's jade pendant.

40:32.410 --> 40:33.380
You have met my mother?

40:33.380 --> 40:35.300
Is she trapped here by Cui Shao'an?

40:35.300 --> 40:36.900
I hid Her Highness.

40:37.980 --> 40:39.790
I know you are Xie Jiayu

40:39.930 --> 40:41.590
because I saved Her Highness.

40:41.780 --> 40:43.900
Her Highness discovered the mines
and could have escaped,

40:43.900 --> 40:45.420
but to save the girls in the mines,

40:45.420 --> 40:46.620
she ended up in danger

40:46.920 --> 40:48.720
and was hunted down by my father.

40:59.380 --> 41:01.340
Her Highness asked me to write to you.

41:01.340 --> 41:04.130
She said that as long as the letter was
delivered to Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

41:04.130 --> 41:05.300
the Heir of Prince Jing'an, Xiao Wuyi,

41:05.300 --> 41:08.080
would figure out that
she was in danger in the mine.

41:08.080 --> 41:09.860
I just didn't expect you to come, too.

41:09.860 --> 41:10.820
Since you are already here...

41:10.820 --> 41:12.490
So you want to make a move tonight?

41:12.490 --> 41:13.950
I have spread the news that

41:14.260 --> 41:16.900
the Heir of Prince Jing'an and Lady Jiayu
have escaped from Lingfeng Fort.

41:16.900 --> 41:19.610
Now, my brother has recovered
from the needle poison.

41:19.610 --> 41:22.170
He will definitely go out of the city
to catch you.

41:22.170 --> 41:24.370
Whoever catches Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu

41:24.490 --> 41:26.690
will be rewarded with 100 taels of gold!

41:28.220 --> 41:31.900
That will be the perfect chance
to bring down my father.
